Description: Processes and analyzes eye-tracking data from EyeLink 1000 Plus
    (remote mode) experiments. Ingests MATLAB .mat files and ASC files,
    applies calibration offsets, computes zone-of-uncertainty metrics,
    binarizes gaze into on/off-task indicators, and performs model-free
    and model-based analyses with behavioral integration.
